<!DOCTYPE ui:UiBinder SYSTEM "http://dl.google.com/gwt/DTD/xhtml.ent">
<ui:UiBinder xmlns:ui="urn:ui:com.google.gwt.uibinder"
	xmlns:g="urn:import:com.google.gwt.user.client.ui" xmlns:d="urn:import:io.github.sidney3172.doc.client">

    <ui:style>
        .snippet{
            font-family: Courier New;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }
    </ui:style>

	<d:Section>
		<h2>Getting started</h2>
		<h3>Inlude gwt-chartjs</h3>
		<p>Gwt-chartjs library available at Maven Central, so if you use Maven as a build system just add new dependency to your project:</p>
        <textarea onclick="this.select()" rows="5" cols="40" style="width: 100%" class="{style.snippet}" ui:field="dependencyCode"></textarea>
		
		<h3>Setup GWT project</h3>
		<p>To make this library available in your GWT project add inherit tag to your .gwt.xml file:</p>
        <textarea onclick="this.select()" rows="1" cols="40" style="width: 100%" class="{style.snippet}" ui:field="inheritCode"></textarea>
	</d:Section>
</ui:UiBinder> 